{"tid":1403421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊入黎震蕩腦袋","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T19:12:04.000Z","uid":89419,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b608d5278f5ded69c764bc28ba35b2c7cb8afb0e","tid":1403421,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:31.000Z","msg":"今日黃大仙街坊無裝上陣，打宿舍，be water霸馬路的確好野<br />\n不過我睇睇下直播諗到個新招<br />\n大家討論下 睇下可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n話説佔龍翔期間有架石油氣車經過<br />\n我就忽發奇想<br />\n諗如果啲狗咁都夠膽放催淚就真真正正攬炒<br />\n轉一轉諗法<br />\n如果我地每次佔領嘅地方係付近有油站主要幹道e.g.觀塘道，告士打道<br />\n有咩事退翻去油站防線<br />\n啲狗都應該唔敢用所有火力武器<br />\n咁就真正佔得有意義啦<br />\n<br />\n只係忽發奇想嘅遊戲攻略，觀迎各位打機能手指正"},{"pid":"dd3873b8f072ae6ec3913bfaebebe5296e456573","tid":1403421,"uid":89419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"二黎仲可以令到啲車冇得入油<br />\n被迫停駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d70f715ae16cff76cc1287182fd1951ea1722d","tid":1403421,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"979e3e213dd57da66805484f5b841a3d3676aa9e","tid":1403421,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:56:51.000Z","msg":"非《一次又一次難清場》<br />\n是《一次又一次難拉人》"},{"pid":"6c4d6968216838e5b633ab44c470de2f6145a49c","tid":1403421,"uid":14835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"但係如果班狗癲到照射入去，入面班義士咪仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9063584ec648f8e421643a9d7663213defdea587","tid":1403421,"uid":89419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6c4d6968216838e5b633ab44c470de2f6145a49c","tid":1403421,"uid":14835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"但係如果班狗癲到照射入去，入面班義士咪仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:00:19.000Z","msg":"一個油站炸起上黎<br />\n應該200m內都仆街<b